translate ru strings:

    old "Sarah leaned closer towards the goblin."
    new "Sarah leaned closer towards the goblin."

    old "She lowered her own voice, speaking in a whisper."
    new "She lowered her own voice, speaking in a whisper."

    old "If you help me escape, I'll promise I'll make sure that the humans in the town won't hurt you."
    new "If you help me escape, I'll promise I'll make sure that the humans in the town won't hurt you."

    old "Raza\" \"Good. Good."
    new "Raza\" \"Good. Good."

    old "What is your name?"
    new "What is your name?"

    old "Raza\" \"They call me Raza. What is your name?"
    new "Raza\" \"They call me Raza. What is your name?"

    old "Now...can you get me out of here?"
    new "Now...can you get me out of here?"

    old "Raza shook his head."
    new "Raza shook his head."

    old "Raza\" \"No. Not now. Too many orc around. They will hear."
    new "Raza\" \"No. Not now. Too many orc around. They will hear."

    old "Sarah felt her heart sink. How much longer would she be trapped here?"
    new "Sarah felt her heart sink. How much longer would she be trapped here?"

    old "When can we escape?"
    new "When can we escape?"

    old "Raza\" \"Orc have feast tonight."
    new "Raza\" \"Orc have feast tonight."

    old "Raza\" \"I serve them extra strong wine. Then we escape."
    new "Raza\" \"I serve them extra strong wine. Then we escape."

    old "The idea of escaping her tonight made her heart rush."
    new "The idea of escaping her tonight made her heart rush."

    old "Okay...I'll wait."
    new "Okay...I'll wait."

    old "The goblin handed her an extra piece of bread."
    new "The goblin handed her an extra piece of bread."

    old "Raza\" \"Eat. You need strength for tonight."
    new "Raza\" \"Eat. You need strength for tonight."

    old "Raza\" \"Travel will be hard."
    new "Raza\" \"Travel will be hard."

    old "Sarah nodded as she eagerly accepted the second piece of bread."
    new "Sarah nodded as she eagerly accepted the second piece of bread."

    old "As she watched the goblin leave, she sat down in her cell again, praying for the next to come soon."
    new "As she watched the goblin leave, she sat down in her cell again, praying for the next to come soon."

    old "Sarah didn't know when she had fallen asleep again."
    new "Sarah didn't know when she had fallen asleep again."

    old "She woke to a sudden sound at the edge of her cage."
    new "She woke to a sudden sound at the edge of her cage."

    old "When she looked up, she saw the goblin had returned, as promised."
    new "When she looked up, she saw the goblin had returned, as promised."

    old "Raza\" \"Sarah, you wake!"
    new "Raza\" \"Sarah, you wake!"

    old "It voice was sharp."
    new "It voice was sharp."

    old "Sarah crawled up from the ground and towards the bars."
    new "Sarah crawled up from the ground and towards the bars."

    old "Raza! Are we ready to go?"
    new "Raza! Are we ready to go?"

    old "Raza\" \"I gave strong wine. Orcs don't know which way is up."
    new "Raza\" \"I gave strong wine. Orcs don't know which way is up."

    old "He held up a small bag."
    new "He held up a small bag."

    old "Raza\" \"I brought clothes. Food. We ready to go."
    new "Raza\" \"I brought clothes. Food. We ready to go."

    old "She couldn't believe that this tiny goblin would prove to be her salvation."
    new "She couldn't believe that this tiny goblin would prove to be her salvation."

    old "How are we going to break this lock?"
    new "How are we going to break this lock?"

    old "The goblin suddenly shook its head."
    new "The goblin suddenly shook its head."

    old "Raza\" \"No. Not yet."
    new "Raza\" \"No. Not yet."

    old "What do you mean? We have to leave tonight, right?"
    new "What do you mean? We have to leave tonight, right?"

    old "Raza\" \"Yes."
    new "Raza\" \"Yes."

    old "Then suddenly, it reached for the ragged loincloth that covered its lower body."
    new "Then suddenly, it reached for the ragged loincloth that covered its lower body."

    old "Sarah nearly jumped back as she saw the creature's erection poke out from underneath."
    new "Sarah nearly jumped back as she saw the creature's erection poke out from underneath."

    old "What...what are you doing?!"
    new "What...what are you doing?!"

    old "She couldn't help her voice from rising, so great was the shock."
    new "She couldn't help her voice from rising, so great was the shock."

    old "Raza\" \"Raza help Sarah. Sarah help Raza."
    new "Raza\" \"Raza help Sarah. Sarah help Raza."

    old "The creature poked its member through the bars, an impressive size given the creature's stature."
    new "The creature poked its member through the bars, an impressive size given the creature's stature."

    old "Give into Raza's demand"
    new "Give into Raza's demand"

    old "Scold him"
    new "Scold him"

    old "Sarah gritted her teeth, angry at what the small creature dared to demand of her."
    new "Sarah gritted her teeth, angry at what the small creature dared to demand of her."

    old "Her situation might be dire, but she would not allow herself to be blackmailed by this thing."
    new "Her situation might be dire, but she would not allow herself to be blackmailed by this thing."

    old "Sarah sat back down on the floor of her cell and lowered her head."
    new "Sarah sat back down on the floor of her cell and lowered her head."

    old "She had been a fool to trust anyone, let alone such a lowly creature that she barely knew."
    new "She had been a fool to trust anyone, let alone such a lowly creature that she barely knew."

    old "Of course he'd try to take advantage of the moment."
    new "Of course he'd try to take advantage of the moment."

    old "That's what they did."
    new "That's what they did."

    old "That's what they all did."
    new "That's what they all did."

